WEBVTT

00:01.485 --> 00:03.502
<i> -Previously on</i> The Resident...
-It's multiple sclerosis.

00:03.653 --> 00:04.670
You will get better.

00:05.414 --> 00:07.914
I actually want a child.
Would you give me

00:08.067 --> 00:08.990
one of your eggs?

00:09.585 --> 00:11.552
You want me
to be your sperm donor?

00:13.405 --> 00:14.996
<i> AUSTIN:</i>
<i> I don't like being alone.</i>

00:15.016 --> 00:17.725
I want to be a father.

00:18.502 --> 00:19.184
<i> IAN:</i>
<i> Hi.</i>

00:19.520 --> 00:21.169
I'm here
to save my daughter's life.

00:21.247 --> 00:22.095
Who are you again?

00:22.264 --> 00:23.480
You only get one father.

00:24.508 --> 00:25.691
<i> BILLIE:</i>
<i> So, the two of you...</i>

00:25.842 --> 00:26.933
Oh, we're friends.

00:27.086 --> 00:27.985
We're also friends.

00:28.954 --> 00:29.611
So far.

00:52.795 --> 00:54.511
(creaking)

00:59.209 --> 01:03.136
