01:03.289 --> 01:07.048
♪<i> Pocket full of posies</i> ♪

01:07.142 --> 01:10.903
♪<i> Ashes, ashes</i> ♪

01:11.054 --> 01:14.798
♪<i> We all fall down</i> ♪

01:14.817 --> 01:19.152
♪<i> Ring around the rosies</i> ♪

